ussia</a>&#160;/</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/New_Silesia" title="New Silesia">New Silesia</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Third_Partition_of_Poland" title="Third Partition of Poland">1795</a>)</small></span></div>
