Vienna</a> <a href="/wiki/Congress_of_Vienna" title="Congress of Vienna">(1814–15)</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;padding:0.25em 0; line-height:1.3em;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Brandenburg" title="Province of Brandenburg">Brandenburg</a>&#160;<b>·</b> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Pomerania" title="Province of Pomerania">Pomerania</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Grand_Duchy_of_Posen" title="Grand Duchy of Posen">Grand Duchy of Posen</a><sup><small>1</small></sup>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Saxony" title="Province of Saxony">Saxony</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Silesia" title="Province of Silesia">Silesia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Westphalia" title="Province of Westphalia">Westphalia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rhine_Province" title="Rhine Province">Rhine Province</a><sup><small>2</small></sup> <small>(1822)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Prussia" title="Province of Prussia">Province of Prussia</a> <small>(1824–78)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Hohenzollern" title="Province of Hohenzollern">Hohenzollern</a> <small>(1850)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Schleswig-Holstein" title="Province of Schleswig-Holstein">Schleswig-Holstein</a>&#160;/</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Province_of_Hanover" title="Province of Hanover">Hanover</a>&#160;/</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Hesse-Nassau" title="Hesse-Nassau">Hesse-Nassau</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Peace_of_Prague_(1866)" title="Peace of Prague (1866)">1866–68</a>)</small></span></div>
